Functionalities:

void SortIntMatrix(int matrix[], int size) ->  Function for sort int arrays of one dimension (Bubblesort)

void InvSortIntMatrix(int matrix[], int size) -> Function for sort int arrays of one dimension (biggest first) (Bubblesort)

void SortDoubleMatrix(double matrix[], int size) -> Function for sort double arrays of one dimension (Bubblesort)

void InvSortDoubleMatrix(double matrix[], int size) -> Function for sort double arrays of one dimension (biggest first) (Bubblesort)
